748
01:44:55,040 --> 01:44:55,360
Koliko to?

749
01:44:56,000 --> 01:44:57,680
Sati 45 skoro.

750
01:44:58,000 --> 01:45:00,720
Dobro smo danas mi to odvozili.

751
01:45:00,880 --> 01:45:01,920
Svašta smo dotaknuli.

752
01:45:02,000 --> 01:45:03,920
Još jedan put hvala, hvala vam što nas gledate.

753
01:45:04,080 --> 01:45:06,960
Naravno da i admirala treba premotati pa iz početka.

754
01:45:07,600 --> 01:45:08,960
Dva puta barem poslušati.

755
01:45:09,200 --> 01:45:09,680
Vidimo se.
